    "slot_size": 208,
    "data_size": 204,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "Rrrrgh,[SP]it's[SP]one[SP]thing[SP]after[SP]another...![1205][001E][SP]Fine!\nArmy[SP]or[SP]no[SP]army,[SP]we're[SP]goin'[SP]after[SP]them!",
